arts.ttl: Preview: Lens vs. Saint-Etienne - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Sunday's Ligue 1 clash between Lens and Saint-Etienne, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.

Lens were unable to follow up successive victories over Marseille and Rennes as they fell to a 1-0 loss to Lille last time out. They should feel confident about returning to winning ways this weekend....
